module RegFile(
    input logic [5:0] RA1,
    input logic [5:0] RA2,
    input logic [5:0] WA,
    input logic [31:0] WD,
    input logic clk,
    input logic WE1,
    output logic [31:0] RD1,
    output logic [31:0] RD2
    );
    logic [31:0] register [63:0];
    always_ff @ (negedge clk) begin
        RD1 = register[RA1];
        RD2 = register[RA2];
    end
    
    always_ff @ (posedge clk) begin
        if (WE1) begin
        register[WA] <= WD;
        end
    end
endmodule

module FullAdder(
    input logic op1,
    input logic op2,
    input logic cin,
    input logic [2:0] opsel,
    output logic result,
    output logic cout
    );
    
    assign result = (opsel == 3'b000) ? op1 + op2 + cin : //ADD
                    (opsel == 3'b011) ? op1 + ~op2 + cin ://SUB
                    (opsel == 3'b010) ? op1 : //MOVE
                    (opsel == 3'b100) ? op1 : //LOAD
                    (opsel == 3'b110) ? op1 : 1'bz; //STORE    
                    
    assign cout =   (opsel == 3'b000) ? (op1&op2)|(op1&cin)|(op2&cin) :
                    (opsel == 3'b011) ? (op1&~op2)|(op1&cin)|(~op2&cin) : 1'b0;         
       

endmodule
